    General stores or mom-n-pop shops are known as 'kiranas' in most parts of the country. It is a form of traditional retail where it offers a wide range of products. Now with the emergence of the various forms of modern retail, many of these establishments are evolving from its traditional format to a more modern, department store format. These shops and establishments are a part of the distributor network of FMCG brands and companies selling a wide range of products. The vast list of general store items does not limit to food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Catering to the convenience of their customers, these shops also extend free home delivery service. Aiming for the convenience of the locals, these general stores also offer complimentary doorstep delivery services. Mentioned above is a vast list of General Stores in Mira Bhayandar Road-Mira Road, Mumbai.
